    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  Using the children\u2019s toy, Shrinky-Dink \u00a9, we present an aptamer-based electrochemical (E-AB) assay that recognizes the spike protein of SARS-CoV-2 in saliva for viral infection detection. The low-cost electrodes are implementable at population scale and demonstrate detection down to 0.1 fg mL\n                  <jats:sup>\u22121</jats:sup>\n                  of the S1 subunit of the spike protein.\n                </jats:p>",
